Hello @here and @Node!

We're releasing `v1.19.1` of the Smart Node. It contains a bug fix and many quality of life updates.

This is a recommend upgrade for all users **and a required update for the <@&886163752553164830>**. This version implements the changes defined on RPIP-77, making minipools use the latest delegate automatically. 

**IF YOU DO NOT WISH TO OPT INTO USING THE LATEST DELEGATE CONTRACT ON YOUR MINIPOOLS, you should not install this version!**

<https://github.com/rocket-pool/smartnode/releases/tag/v1.19.1>

## Client Updates
- Besu updated to v26.1.0;
- Nimbus updated to v26.1.0;

## Smart Node Updates:
- Fix selecting rewards ruleset for the approximator;
- Add a task to automatically submit txs for minipools to use the latest delegate. See [RPIP-77](https://rpips.rocketpool.net/RPIPs/RPIP-77) for more details;
- Add option to send all tokens from the node wallet. If ETH is selected a tiny gas reserve will be kept.
- Add option to exit multiple validators from the queue;
- Improve the gas estimation for multi deposits so users can send more deposits getting closer to the tx gas limit;
- Use `usableCredit` when calculating the remaining amount to be sent for partial credit deposits;
- Add the `assign-deposits`  command;
- Show the queue position when selecting validators to exit;
- Show the estimate queue position when depositing, so users can better choose when to use express tickets;

To install it, please follow our Smart Node upgrade guide here: <https://docs.rocketpool.net/node-staking/updates#updating-the-smartnode-stack>

Thanks everyone!

